      "writtenOn": "2020-03-16T19:59:53Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Just for my info, so we\u0027re going to track wasted space as \"totalUsableSpace - totalSpaceInUse\" ?",
      "revId": "bf5984699f82929125f744af1fed887f4f123051",
      "serverId": "5086850b-e599-37d2-8ec8-ff16aeccbf02",
